            <li>Built Power BI/Excel dashboards tracking fraud by route, crew, and category with real‑time KPIs and historical benchmarking.</li>
            <li>Collaborated with clients to scope UI/UX changes and ship tailored front‑end features (Angular) via Agile sprints in Jira.</li>
            <li>Supported AWS S3 content deployment for airline apps and contributed across onboarding to release cycles.</li>
